// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0083 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 9930fe9d-e044-56d8-96bf-824a553f89fd

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:2.0*")
